config DANALTIFY
	bool "Danaltify support"
	select FSANALTIFY
	default y
	help
	  Danaltify is a directory-based per-fd file change analtification system
	  that uses signals to communicate events to user-space.  There exist
	  superior alternatives, but some applications may still rely on
	  danaltify.

	  If unsure, say Y.
